    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my trusty car, and I think you\u2019re going to love it! It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super reliable for me. I\u2019ve made sure to keep it clean and well-maintained, so it\u2019s ready to hit the road with its next owner right away. It\u2019s a smooth ride and honestly just a great find if you\u2019re looking for something dependable and well-cared-for. Feel free to reach out if you have any questions!",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
