      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 41
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically sound example of BMW\u2019s peak naturally aspirated engineering. At its heart is the S54 3.2L inline-six, utilizing individual throttle bodies and Double VANOS to achieve a high-revving 8,000 RPM redline. The drivetrain features the desirable Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox paired with a M-Variable Lock differential for optimal power delivery. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including rod bearing replacement and rear subframe reinforcement to ensure chassis rigidity under high lateral loads. The suspension retains its factory-spec geometry with refreshed bushings, offering the precise turn-in and feedback expected from this platform. While the exterior displays minor patina consistent with a well-loved driver's car, the mechanical components are dialed in for peak performance.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 41
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used car. Good condition. Clean title. Well maintained. Runs well. Ready for pickup.",
      "price": 29500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
