    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "This E46 M3 features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies and a high-revving 8,000 RPM redline. The chassis remains taut with a reinforced rear subframe and updated bushings, ensuring the variable M differential lock translates every horse to the tarmac. Equipped with a crisp 6-speed manual transmission, the mechanical engagement is unparalleled. Recent VANOS service and valve adjustment ensure the valvetrain operates with factory precision. Minor aesthetic imperfections consistent with age do not detract from its formidable lateral grip and balanced 50/50 weight distribution.",
